{"id": "ChIJE42BIEm_woAREnla82E_qHk", "rating": 4.7, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 355, "displayName": {"text": "Mashti Malone's", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJE42BIEm_woAREnla82E_qHk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5a1MzUjZZVGRMU0VRNE9HMDVXRXBKV21aQmRWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "BEST ICE CREAM IN LA. Hands down. Both the classic American flavors and some incredible (and much older recipes!) Persian options. Some personal favorites include Herbal Snow, Faloodeh, and cookies and cream (with or without mint).\n\nJust one little request…please make a saffron ice cream without nuts for those who can’t eat ‘em! 🙏", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "BEST ICE CREAM IN LA. Hands down. Both the classic American flavors and some incredible (and much older recipes!) Persian options. Some personal favorites include Herbal Snow, Faloodeh, and cookies and cream (with or without mint).\n\nJust one little request…please make a saffron ice cream without nuts for those who can’t eat ‘em! 🙏", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kim Trail", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101849020341398533588/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ5v-ukIqbKjndzrDpPRvUEpEiZ758OsFyHFfLWRVsNjQMj0w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-25T23:53:07.217501822Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5a1MzUjZZVGRMU0VRNE9HMDVXRXBKV21aQmRWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5a1MzUjZZVGRMU0VRNE9HMDVXRXBKV21aQmRWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf4920818d13:0x79a83f61f35a7912"}, {"name": "places/ChIJE42BIEm_woAREnla82E_qHk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pJM1N6Vm1aMnhZU1VSU2FFZFJVVlo0YUZZek0yYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "You would never expect this little place to be such a gem. The ice cream was amazing and unique. Very creamy. A few vegan flavors too. Even creamy ones.\nMy saffron pistachio and my mom's rose water were amazing.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "You would never expect this little place to be such a gem. The ice cream was amazing and unique. Very creamy. A few vegan flavors too. Even creamy ones.\nMy saffron pistachio and my mom's rose water were amazing.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Sara Sparkles", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107867457615974242321/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUswUkkNz_YcnrcKVh2v7EV45b8u15wkFOzSn3It3DWL2nEj4Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-05T00:56:57.684604567Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pJM1N6Vm1aMnhZU1VSU2FFZFJVVlo0YUZZek0yYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pJM1N6Vm1aMnhZU1VSU2FFZFJVVlo0YUZZek0yYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf4920818d13:0x79a83f61f35a7912"}, {"name": "places/ChIJE42BIEm_woAREnla82E_qHk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20welNWTnRNWGhQYUZCSWJIZHdTVEEwWVZkNlNIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Great ice cream, interesting flavors. Subtle and enjoyable; you find yourself sitting and focusing on the taste. Saffron and pistachio is a must try.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Great ice cream, interesting flavors. Subtle and enjoyable; you find yourself sitting and focusing on the taste. Saffron and pistachio is a must try.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Omar", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114890073114524626247/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJA52_H_LMONBDBTPJbQM_jjzjFD0f9q6vHllgNefq8Hwmo7g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-17T00:33:50.912756294Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20welNWTnRNWGhQYUZCSWJIZHdTVEEwWVZkNlNIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20welNWTnRNWGhQYUZCSWJIZHdTVEEwWVZkNlNIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf4920818d13:0x79a83f61f35a7912"}, {"name": "places/ChIJE42BIEm_woAREnla82E_qHk/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VOeWw4cDJyLWNfNGxRRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "I really like this ice cream place! The quality of the ice cream is excellent, and they offer a wide variety of flavors. Some are truly unique—like pistachio with saffron and lavender coconut—and many of them taste amazing. A few are more of an acquired taste, but the staff is happy to let you sample flavors before you decide, which is a big plus.\n\nPayment is easy and convenient—they accept credit cards, cash, Apple Pay, and other forms of NFC payment. While the indoor seating is limited, there are a few spots to sit outside. There’s also plenty of parking available in the lot, which is great.\n\nOne downside is that they don’t have a restroom for customers, so keep that in mind. But overall, I’d definitely recommend giving this place a try. The prices are fair, and the ice cream is worth it!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I really like this ice cream place! The quality of the ice cream is excellent, and they offer a wide variety of flavors. Some are truly unique—like pistachio with saffron and lavender coconut—and many of them taste amazing. A few are more of an acquired taste, but the staff is happy to let you sample flavors before you decide, which is a big plus.\n\nPayment is easy and convenient—they accept credit cards, cash, Apple Pay, and other forms of NFC payment. While the indoor seating is limited, there are a few spots to sit outside. There’s also plenty of parking available in the lot, which is great.\n\nOne downside is that they don’t have a restroom for customers, so keep that in mind. But overall, I’d definitely recommend giving this place a try. The prices are fair, and the ice cream is worth it!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Savio Pinto", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116293884867235786700/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFS5l4k7am7WZr6i1gCoZZ2A7jsQFpzHl3zDpgxRCF8XBOC-DCMg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-05-25T20:32:38.875003Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VOeWw4cDJyLWNfNGxRRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VOeWw4cDJyLWNfNGxRRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf4920818d13:0x79a83f61f35a7912"}, {"name": "places/ChIJE42BIEm_woAREnla82E_qHk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WNVdVVmtXazFtT1VkbFYwaHlNQzFPWlZJMlQxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "First timer! So many different flavors!! They are famous for their saffron ice cream but The cucumber is my favorite. Must visit when you’re in the area!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "First timer! So many different flavors!! They are famous for their saffron ice cream but The cucumber is my favorite. Must visit when you’re in the area!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Shirley Jiang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113382117883479536466/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWG5qy8DvIiWc2d439u97bnyZ6zEtG9f3f73DGrKirGKOQf3_xP=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-04T05:34:45.387373316Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WNVdVVmtXazFtT1VkbFYwaHlNQzFPWlZJMlQxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.goo